      </introduction>
      <task>
        <statement>
          <p>
            Fia earns 3 points every time she finds a star in her <pubtitle>Dora the Explorer</pubtitle> game. She earns a one-time bonus of 50 points in each level for finding a banana for her monkey friend, Boots. Based on the number of stars she finds, how many points will Fia earn in a level if she always finds the banana?
          </p>
